Jans Rautenbach (22 Febụwarị 1936 2 Nọvemba 2016) bụ odee ihe nkiri si South Africa, onye na-emepụta ihe nkiri na onye nduzi. Ihe nkiri ya nke 1968 bụ Die Kandidaat gosipụtara esemokwu ma nweta ụfọdụ nyocha na South Africa, n'ihi nkatọ a na-ahụ maka usoro ịkpa ókè agbụrụ. Ihe nkiri ikpeazụ ya, Abraham, bụ ihe na-ewu ewu na ụlọ ọrụ South Africa.
